RICHMOND COUNCIL SUBMITS PLANNING APPLICATION FOR TWICKENHAM RIVERSIDE REDEVELOPMENT
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    A Planning Application to redevelop Twickenham Riverside has been
    submitted and will be open to statutory consultation.

    Over the past two years the Council has been consulting
    with residents and businesses in Twickenham on proposals for a new
    development on King Street / Water Lane and Twickenham Riverside.
    The development site includes three properties on the corner of
    King Street and Water Lane, the car park to the rear and the
    derelict former swimming pool buildings.

