NORTHCOTE NATURE RESERVE INAUGURATED WITH TREE PLANTING
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    On Sunday 3rd December, local residents planted eight trees to mark
    the inauguration of the new Northcote Nature Reserve in Isleworth.

    The Nature Reserve is the northernmost point of the recently
    announced Lower Crane Restoration Project, which aims to restore 3m
    of riverside paths and create a more natural river along the
    adjacent river Crane.

