20MPH LIMIT COULD BE INTRODUCED ACROSS BOROUGH
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    A 20mph speed limit could be introduced across the borough it was
    announced at last week's Council meeting.

    The plans were announced by Cllr Peter Buckwell, Richmond Council
    Cabinet Member for Highways, following a rise in the number
    of community petitions being submitted to the Council,
